@node m3 "Quit"

 Quit TB4.0.  Any unsaved data will be lost!

 Save your data before you Quit.

 @{" Save File " link b4}
 @{" The Menus " link m1}

@endnode


@node m4 "Delete"

 Delete a file.

 Lets you select a file to delete and delete it.

 When you have selected a file you will be asked if you are sure you want
 to delete it.  This is your LAST chance to stop the file being deleted.

 @{fg shine}Warning@{fg text} You can't get back what you delete.
         Be careful when using this function.

 @{" The Menus " link m1}

@endnode
